Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.46,0:00:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday... Yes, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be walking down
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,a spring path while looking up at the\Ncherry blossoms whether I want to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.04,0:00:15.34,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 12: 'Friends and Love,\NLove and Cherry Blossoms'"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a normal person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.68,0:00:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have the ability to\Ntouch something I can't see,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.10,0:00:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't involve myself in something\Nthat's not happening right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm scared of is while I'm not looking
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.19,0:00:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura will change into something different.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've made up my mind to spend\Nevery spare moment looking at Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.29,0:00:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:50.32,On Top,,0,0,0,,Pssh, pssh, pssh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Heyo, Shima!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.80,0:00:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Adachicchi is with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.05,0:00:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hino and Nagafuji. It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.01,0:01:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It sure has!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.31,0:01:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you change your shampoo, Nagafuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I spent the night\Nat Hino's place yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.90,0:01:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and took a bath there this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.11,0:01:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you don't really\Nhave to talk about that now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.82,0:01:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, it's our turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.95,0:01:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.04,0:01:24.62,On Top,,0,0,0,,Pssh, pssh, pssh, pssh, pssh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Staying at someone's house...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then using their bath and then\Nheading right to school...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Can I come over, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.51,0:01:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And spend the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.09,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, at Hino's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.77,0:01:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Your place, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.06,0:01:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.94,0:01:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.11,0:01:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, our bathtub's tiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.99,0:02:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really care about the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.07,0:02:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, do I? No, I think it does matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.46,0:02:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it does matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.67,0:02:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't really matter...\NBut I want to spend the night!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.51,0:02:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Because I want to be\Ncloser to you, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are we not close already? I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.23,0:02:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, we are, we are!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.23,0:02:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... But I want to be closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.57,0:02:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you get closer by spending the night, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.46,0:02:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.76,0:03:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Under the pretense of discussing\Nme spending the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to hang out with Shimamura\Nafter school... Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Spending the night is awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to come over to\Nmy place this Saturday or Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Two days off...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.86,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And spending the night two nights...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stay at my place that long?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.45,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so you know, my place isn't an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What about work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to work... um, from your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.92,0:03:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.92,0:03:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there's probably going to be\None more when we get to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure why, but it feels like\NI have two or three little sisters now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Her little sister... Shimamura Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.19,0:03:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like an alliteration.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.61,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd be even closer than friends then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,and that part's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.57,0:04:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But then I think we'd get too close\Nand she'd notice me even less.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.04,0:04:14.08,OS,,0,0,0,,"Change of underwear\NSocks 4? 5?\NPJs (Under shirt and track pants)\NFood: Bread & Instant ramen"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's all the stuff I'll need to buy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.29,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, I just need something to\Nmake sure Shimamura doesn't get bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.26,0:04:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's not going to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can't think of anything to do,\NI guess we can just watch TV together.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.61,0:04:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The same thing will happen and hopefully,\NI won't run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh... You seem to have a lot of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You do realize you're not moving, right?\NIt's a bit much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, aren't you early? It's still 8 AM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry. Were you sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.15,0:05:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, you woke me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so punctual, Adachi. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.66,0:05:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I was actually here at 7 AM,\Nbut I figured that was a bit too early.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.79,0:05:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't tell her I was just wandering\Naround on my bike for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.59,0:05:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's probably the only\Nweird part of this, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.89,0:05:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.43,0:05:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.40,0:06:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You remember my friend, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.78,0:06:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,She's being a good girl today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the room upstairs okay? Or well...\NThat's the only open room we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Did you not want to go upstairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.67,0:06:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I won't be staying\Nin the same room as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.80,0:06:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to stay in the same room as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.77,0:06:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it, but I don't think\Nmy little sister will like that. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There was no way this was\Nall going to go as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.07,0:06:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if Shimamura's okay\Nwith me staying in her room...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.20,0:06:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it, but I don't think\Nmy little sister will like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine with it... I'm fine with it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.75,0:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.92,0:07:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to do for breakfast?\NDid you already eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.97,0:07:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I came prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:19.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Long Long Sticks"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? My cooking's not good enough for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.40,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I'll have some. Thank you very much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dig in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Adachi,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.07,0:07:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you probably actually go to school\Nunlike this daughter of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi's in the same boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.08,0:07:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,She looks like a nice, quiet girl,\Nunlike my delinquent over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's more of a good girl than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good girl...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you must be older, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.15,0:08:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the grub.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.25,0:08:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.75,0:08:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, earlier? My mom's always like that,\Nso there's no point in getting mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.85,0:08:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's just how their relationship is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.18,0:08:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,More importantly, Adachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.86,0:08:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how long it's been\Nsince I was able to feel
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that days off were actually special?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:09:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday, the first day I stayed over,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.16,0:09:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,really did end with nothing happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing special with Shimamura\Nactually happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just there together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:26.35,On Top,,0,0,0,,Meat was really cheap\Nat the supermarket today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Just being with her might\Njust be ideal to me, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.78,0:09:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm going to do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.00,0:09:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.29,0:09:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura laughed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.71,0:09:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Today might be a good day after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.92,0:09:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.93,0:10:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not like absolutely\Nnothing happened yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.35,0:10:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hogetsu, hurry up, and take a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You go right to bed whenever you get full.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.23,0:10:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? You brought that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's room is on the first floor,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but she naturally came to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.45,0:10:30.69,On Top,,0,0,0,,You're too polite, Adachi.\NYou could've just used ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.65,0:10:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That made me so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.69,0:10:35.19,On Top,,0,0,0,,B-But I wanted to cause you\Nthe least amount of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not exactly towards who,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,but I felt superior towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.38,0:10:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I got a little bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.56,0:10:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I... um, sit between your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.11,0:10:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,run away this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.49,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't mind if I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.54,0:11:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not going to scooch closer?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.88,0:11:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Then, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.30,0:11:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So soft... Eek.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-There's no reason to panic.\NShimamura's a girl, but so am I... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she does fall asleep\Nright after eating...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:12:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's up? Why do you have\Na change of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to take one first? That's rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take one together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where'd that come from?\NI thought you said you're embarrassed to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay sometimes... Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.90,0:12:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.61,0:12:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'm going...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop daydreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.96,0:12:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.80,0:12:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. Thanks for having me over...\Nor maybe I should say, "I'm home."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.76,0:12:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.64,0:12:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I've returned...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.89,0:12:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter's out right now.\NShe said something about shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She should be back soon, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.32,0:13:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,She can be pretty lazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.03,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,She's always been a sleepyhead\Never since she was little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She really does sleep a lot like a koala.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.67,0:13:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. How's she doing at school?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she actually going to class?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.09,0:13:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.51,0:13:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's good. She tends to be lazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.22,0:13:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so it must be hard to get her to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Not at all. Actually, it's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,She always leads... Is that the right word?\NShe always leads me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home. Oh, welcome back, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.53,0:13:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.95,0:13:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,WB.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.95,0:13:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I see you're both enjoying some {\i1}dango{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.20,0:13:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't say anything weird to her, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess upstairs works.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I think "lead" really was the right term.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.22,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretty much follow Shimamura\Naround like her little puppy dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.06,0:14:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sit there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.98,0:14:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.40,0:14:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, lower your head and bend down a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.15,0:14:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? L-Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.90,0:14:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay just like that for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.83,0:14:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, we go like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And there we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Now you have the same hairstyle as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.97,0:14:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.39,0:14:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair color's starting to match yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.52,0:15:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured we'd end up looking a lot alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.03,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.24,0:15:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we don't look that much alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. You can have that hairclip.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.66,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.58,0:15:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.75,0:15:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.21,0:15:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But that means we're matching!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I... Sh-Shimamura, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I... wuv...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.49,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You look wuvly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Wuvly, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:16:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You look lovely, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We did this before, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.25,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's stretch out those cheeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.14,0:16:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.94,0:16:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So today...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to sleep together today?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.03,0:16:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.66,0:16:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't even hesitate. Then actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.67,0:16:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've suggested this yesterday, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.34,0:16:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But will it be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.10,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister sleeping on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.56,0:17:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she has a friend\Nsleeping over today, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Little?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall teach you about the universe, Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-The universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.87,0:17:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.62,0:17:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,First, my kind tends to live\Nan average of 800 million years,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,so I belong to species\Nthat lives for a much longer time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.92,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm turning off the lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.05,0:17:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.89,0:18:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I was just wondering if you\Nwere really asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.65,0:18:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah. I'm in my futon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.03,0:18:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to grow more\Ndistant with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.86,0:18:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Three, two, one. My courage\Nis trying to tell me to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My courage is taking the initiative,\Nand kicking me in the ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.51,0:18:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell like a bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.30,0:19:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to sleep together?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The universe... The universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.65,0:19:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you like your Big Sis's shoulder pillow?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.19,0:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'm going to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.61,0:19:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair's still a bit wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something about that warmth\Nyou feel when it's wet that feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.87,0:19:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I have my arm back now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.75,0:19:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.09,0:19:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How much longer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.38,0:19:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I fall asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I ever going to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.39,0:19:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah. We're changing desks tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.93,0:19:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? We are?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you didn't know\Nbecause you skipped class.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be great if we could sit this close.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.19,0:20:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, I'm sure there'd be a few\Nproblems if we sat this close...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.66,0:20:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be, will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.63,0:20:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat lunch together tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course. So relax, and go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.68,0:20:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi... Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.82,0:20:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold your horses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Take these with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are these?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Packed lunches are making a comeback!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why though?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.72,0:21:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, why are you such a pain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, I think this is the first time\Nwe've gone to school together.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me sit near Shimamura.\NPlease let me sit near Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me sit near Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.83,0:21:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how much praying\Nactually helps in real life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, eyes up front.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.39,0:21:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess finding that out is half the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.40,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is sorta plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we got that much closer,\Nand we didn't move that much away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:15.46,On Top,,0,0,0,,"Delinquent" "Adachi"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.51,0:22:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And before I knew it, it had already been\Na month since we became second-years.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.96,0:22:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll only have one more April in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.71,0:22:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll be May, then June...\NThe time we have isn't infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.81,0:22:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.52,0:22:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday... Yes, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.48,0:22:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,even if I can't imagine it clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.02,0:22:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the future is inevitable. A world\Nwhere there'll be no spring breaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or perhaps, a future where\Nthere's no one next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be walking down
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.49,0:22:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,a spring path while looking up at the\Ncherry blossoms whether I want to or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.88,0:23:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.01,0:23:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And until then,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.51,0:23:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll settle for the cherry blossom\Nthat's right in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.23,0:23:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't mind it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.15,0:23:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the end of April. There aren't\Nany more cherry blossoms anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why... I'll need Adachi\Nto be my cherry blossom.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.52,0:23:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Her profile will always...
